Title: You go to my head
Writer: Pierre Bourdy, Rosemary Ricchio, Matt Steigbigel (idea), Dimitri de Clercq (idea), Dimitri de Clercq
Actors: Delfine Bafort, Svetozar Cvetkovic, Arend Pinoy, Omar Sarnane
Plot: Following a mysterious car accident in the desert, Dafne suffers from post-traumatic amnesia. Jake, the first person she sees when she regains consciousness, tells her he's her husband.
